No. Please. Don't.

4
00:02:52,371 --> 00:02:55,807
Oh. God. I don't want to die.

5
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:03,004
Yeah. Yeah. I'll make you clean.

6
00:03:08,787 --> 00:03:10,186
I'm sorry.

7
00:03:12,758 --> 00:03:15,022
I didn't mean to...

8
