All these mirrors.

40
00:09:46,193 --> 00:09:49,629
- Best to keep your eyes away from them.
- You polish them!

41
00:09:49,930 --> 00:09:52,831
- I'm sorry!
- The mirrors. They're so clean.

42
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:55,960
No. That's Gary. Gary Lewis.

43
00:09:56,036 --> 00:09:58,470
Fellow who was working here before you.

44
00:09:58,539 --> 00:10:01,007
He was completely obsessed
with these damn mirrors.

45
00:10:01,075 --> 00:10:03,475
Spent the entire night cleaning them.

46
00:10:05,346 --> 00:10:08,281
How long has it been
since you left the NYPD!

47
00:10:10,784 --> 00:10:12,615
