53
00:10:27,668 --> 00:10:29,192
It's all right.

54
00:10:37,511 --> 00:10:41,140
There was a pretty big team
working here before the fire.

55
00:10:41,215 --> 00:10:45,345
You know. When you stop to think.
Of all the department stores in New York.

56
00:10:45,419 --> 00:10:48,855
This one was the most beautiful.
Most luxurious.

57
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:52,850
