most of your time.

60
00:10:58,832 --> 00:11:01,665
At least you got electricity in here.

61
00:11:01,735 --> 00:11:04,169
It's warm. It's nice.

62
00:11:04,238 --> 00:11:05,671
You've even got a TV.

63
00:11:19,453 --> 00:11:23,116
I opened up the trunk,
which he so called hid the pictures.

64
00:11:23,190 --> 00:11:26,057
I grabbed the goody bag,
walked to the backyard,

65
00:11:26,126 --> 00:11:30,187
opened up the barbecue grill,
I grabbed the lighter fluid,

66
00:11:30,264 --> 00:11:31,993
Waiting to Exhale.

67
00:11:33,167 --> 00:11:34,498
Hello!

68
00:11:35,703 --> 00:11:36,727
Hello.

69
00:11:36,804 --> 00:11:39,773
- Hey. Rosa. How are you doing!
- I'm fine. Let me help you.

70
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,205
Thanks.

71
00:11:42,376 --> 00:11:43,502
Where are the kids!

72
00:11:43,577 --> 00:11:46,171
