75
00:11:53,253 --> 00:11:57,747
Which is. Like. One of my best friends.
Which is a boy. Likes me.

76
00:11:57,825 --> 00:12:02,319
And this girl named Christiana.
Who liked him. Is just now gossiping.

77
00:12:02,396 --> 00:12:03,761
