Ben! What happened!

161
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:53,240
Just leave me alone.
Please. Just leave me alone!

162
00:22:53,313 --> 00:22:55,406
Angie. Get out of here! Now!

163
00:23:22,308 --> 00:23:24,401
