187
00:33:44,497 --> 00:33:46,795
- You just had a nightmare. Sweetie.
- Okay.

188
00:33:46,866 --> 00:33:49,164
Sometimes they can feel really real.
But they're not. All right!

189
00:33:49,235 --> 00:33:51,328
