214
00:35:33,606 --> 00:35:35,096
I feel...

215
00:35:36,675 --> 00:35:41,009
I feel like I'm not the one
looking into the mirrors

216
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:43,412
but they're looking back at me.

217
00:35:45,050 --> 00:35:48,577
