- Did they tell you how he died!

241
00:38:41,026 --> 00:38:42,857
No. No. They wouldn't tell me.

242
00:38:42,928 --> 00:38:45,829
Mrs. Sapelli is waiting for me at home.
I got to go.

243
00:38:45,898 --> 00:38:48,128
By the way.
About that leak in the basement.

244
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:52,500
They're sending someone over
to work on that. Beginning of next week.

245
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:25,364
We have a white male. 50 years of age.
Name unknown.

246
00:39:26,205 --> 00:39:28,673
Following the completion
of the external examination.

247
00:39:28,741 --> 00:39:31,301
